{
  "video_id": "z3kdIL_EbQU",
  "title": "The awful logic of land mines -- and an app that helps people avoid them | Carlos Bautista",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13504.0,
      "end_time": 15896.0,
      "text": "When you walk around the place where you live,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15921.0,
      "end_time": 17349.0,
      "text": "most of the times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17374.0,
      "end_time": 19538.0,
      "text": "you feel pretty safe and comfortable, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20839.0,
      "end_time": 23912.0,
      "text": "Now imagine if there were land mines"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23936.0,
      "end_time": 26109.0,
      "text": "buried right here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26133.0,
      "end_time": 27761.0,
      "text": "scattered around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27785.0,
      "end_time": 30269.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;d never know when you might step on one."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32100.0,
      "end_time": 35230.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how it is for many in my home country, Colombia."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35393.0,
      "end_time": 39123.0,
      "text": "As a result of a 50-year internal armed conflict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39147.0,
      "end_time": 41583.0,
      "text": "we have an undetermined number of land mines"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41608.0,
      "end_time": 43504.0,
      "text": "buried throughout the countryside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43529.0,
      "end_time": 46687.0,
      "text": "affecting more than one third of the Colombian population."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48186.0,
      "end_time": 51430.0,
      "text": "These anti-personnel mines"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51454.0,
      "end_time": 54456.0,
      "text": "are designed to maim, not to kill their targets."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55769.0,
      "end_time": 59170.0,
      "text": "The logic behind this, which is awful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59194.0,
      "end_time": 63770.0,
      "text": "is that more resources are taken up caring for an injured soldier"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63794.0,
      "end_time": 66110.0,
      "text": "than dealing with a person who has been killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 67348.0,
      "end_time": 71791.0,
      "text": "I met Adriana Rodriguez about five years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71815.0,
      "end_time": 74820.0,
      "text": "while I was working for the Colombian government"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74106.0,
      "end_time": 76290.0,
      "text": "as a documentary filmmaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76374.0,
      "end_time": 78300.0,
      "text": "During the conflict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78540.0,
      "end_time": 79832.0,
      "text": "she was forced to leave her house ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81268.0,
      "end_time": 83460.0,
      "text": "with her kids in her arms."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84118.0,
      "end_time": 87460.0,
      "text": "One day, one of her neighbors was killed"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87484.0,
      "end_time": 89610.0,
      "text": "while he stepped on a land mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 92406.0,
      "end_time": 96558.0,
      "text": "He was actually inside an abandoned house, not outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96582.0,
      "end_time": 99732.0,
      "text": "a house exactly like the one Adriana was forced to leave."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 100442.0,
      "end_time": 104860.0,
      "text": "Ever since, she has been living with the fear that she, or her children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104885.0,
      "end_time": 106233.0,
      "text": "might step on a land mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 107855.0,
      "end_time": 111680.0,
      "text": "You know, the Colombian conflict has been running for so long"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 111920.0,
      "end_time": 116457.0,
      "text": "that neither me nor my mom have seen our country in peace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 116481.0,
      "end_time": 117949.0,
      "text": "and for someone like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 117973.0,
      "end_time": 121434.0,
      "text": "who has been living detached from all this suffering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 121458.0,
      "end_time": 123353.0,
      "text": "there was only two options:"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124778.0,
      "end_time": 126811.0,
      "text": "either I get used to it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126835.0,
      "end_time": 130857.0,
      "text": "or I can try to change it with all my heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 131989.0,
      "end_time": 134648.0,
      "text": "And I have to admit that for almost 30 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134672.0,
      "end_time": 137631.0,
      "text": "I was getting used to it, you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 138694.0,
      "end_time": 142159.0,
      "text": "But something changed for me when I met my wife."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 142614.0,
      "end_time": 144449.0,
      "text": "She is a political scientist"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 144473.0,
      "end_time": 147583.0,
      "text": "completely passionate about the Colombian armed conflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 148830.0,
      "end_time": 150440.0,
      "text": "She helped me to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 150680.0,
      "end_time": 154440.0,
      "text": "how deeply our country has been affected by land mines and by war."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 155166.0,
      "end_time": 157759.0,
      "text": "We decided to come here to the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 157783.0,
      "end_time": 159831.0,
      "text": "in search of new skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 159855.0,
      "end_time": 164840.0,
      "text": "that would enable us to contribute in a fair way to our society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 164109.0,
      "end_time": 166109.0,
      "text": "and maybe even help heal it."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 167364.0,
      "end_time": 168535.0,
      "text": "While in grad school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 168559.0,
      "end_time": 169769.0,
      "text": "I started developing"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 169793.0,
      "end_time": 172833.0,
      "text": "an augmented reality, really broad application"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 172857.0,
      "end_time": 176165.0,
      "text": "to help military personnel to deactivate land mines more safely."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 177583.0,
      "end_time": 180211.0,
      "text": "During that time, I also realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 180235.0,
      "end_time": 182862.0,
      "text": "that Colombia is not the only country in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182886.0,
      "end_time": 185281.0,
      "text": "that has to worry about land mines."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 186724.0,
      "end_time": 189569.0,
      "text": "In fact, more than 58 countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 189593.0,
      "end_time": 193362.0,
      "text": "are still contaminated with any sort of explosive device."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 194101.0,
      "end_time": 197673.0,
      "text": "Only in 2015, due to an escalation of war"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 197697.0,
      "end_time": 201728.0,
      "text": "in countries like Libya, Syria, Ukraine and Yemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 201752.0,
      "end_time": 204348.0,
      "text": "the number of [land mine casualties] almost doubled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 204372.0,
      "end_time": 210287.0,
      "text": "from 3,695 to 6,461 people."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 211510.0,
      "end_time": 212234.0,
      "text": "Imagine that."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 212259.0,
      "end_time": 215195.0,
      "text": "While some countries are trying to get rid of land mines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 215219.0,
      "end_time": 217638.0,
      "text": "some others are increasing their use."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 218648.0,
      "end_time": 222744.0,
      "text": "But what happens when a conflict that involved land mines"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 222768.0,
      "end_time": 224760.0,
      "text": "comes to an end?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 224782.0,
      "end_time": 226965.0,
      "text": "There are two consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226989.0,
      "end_time": 228648.0,
      "text": "On the one hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 228672.0,
      "end_time": 233359.0,
      "text": "the internally displaced population will start returning to their lands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 233384.0,
      "end_time": 235232.0,
      "text": "and on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 235256.0,
      "end_time": 238891.0,
      "text": "hidden land mines are going to start exploding more often"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238915.0,
      "end_time": 240303.0,
      "text": "on the civilian side."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 241330.0,
      "end_time": 243803.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the reason why I decided to join"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 243827.0,
      "end_time": 246414.0,
      "text": "the Computer Science Department at NYU,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 246438.0,
      "end_time": 249126.0,
      "text": "along with Professor Claudio Silva"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 249151.0,
      "end_time": 251868.0,
      "text": "to start to develop an app called MineSafe."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 252831.0,
      "end_time": 257168.0,
      "text": "MineSafe uses information from the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 258380.0,
      "end_time": 262871.0,
      "text": "to suggest paths that have been declared as the most transited"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 262895.0,
      "end_time": 266529.0,
      "text": "without accident or incident caused by a land mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 267350.0,
      "end_time": 270662.0,
      "text": "These traffic patterns can also be used to determine"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 270686.0,
      "end_time": 273974.0,
      "text": "the top priority zones to be de-mined."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 275666.0,
      "end_time": 280470.0,
      "text": "Almost 15 million people are living now in the countryside of Colombia."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 281850.0,
      "end_time": 285587.0,
      "text": "Imagine, for a moment, if we can crowdsource information from all of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 285611.0,
      "end_time": 288681.0,
      "text": "to help people like Adriana and her children"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 288705.0,
      "end_time": 291198.0,
      "text": "to find safe and reliable paths."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 291222.0,
      "end_time": 293613.0,
      "text": "This information can not only be used for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 294320.0,
      "end_time": 297674.0,
      "text": "This information can also help them to become more productive."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 298379.0,
      "end_time": 300509.0,
      "text": "Farmers will be able to find"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 300533.0,
      "end_time": 304546.0,
      "text": "which lands have been cleared from explosive devices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 304570.0,
      "end_time": 309832.0,
      "text": "and in that way, they will be able to find new, fertile grounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 309857.0,
      "end_time": 311284.0,
      "text": "to start growing food again."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 313212.0,
      "end_time": 316555.0,
      "text": "MineSafe has now a partnership with the Colombian government"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 316579.0,
      "end_time": 318372.0,
      "text": "for the initial pilot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 318396.0,
      "end_time": 322634.0,
      "text": "and we have now some connections with Cambodia and Somalia as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 323485.0,
      "end_time": 325889.0,
      "text": "This project is being funded by private money"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 325913.0,
      "end_time": 327835.0,
      "text": "here in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 327859.0,
      "end_time": 329683.0,
      "text": "but we don&#39;t want to stop here."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 329708.0,
      "end_time": 331232.0,
      "text": "We want to go big,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 331256.0,
      "end_time": 334578.0,
      "text": "and we want to scale the project to every single place"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 334603.0,
      "end_time": 336349.0,
      "text": "where land mines are still a threat."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 338709.0,
      "end_time": 343231.0,
      "text": "The Colombian armed conflict is finally coming to an end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 343255.0,
      "end_time": 347986.0,
      "text": "but the consequences of years of war are still buried under our feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 348887.0,
      "end_time": 354167.0,
      "text": "We at MineSafe are working to help both people and land"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 354191.0,
      "end_time": 355433.0,
      "text": "to find peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 355848.0,
      "end_time": 356999.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 357230.0,
      "end_time": 362420.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}